# TrackiFi — Comprehensive UI/UX Development Plan

> **Platform**: Expo (React Native) + Web via Expo Router  
> **Backend**: Cloudflare Workers (Hono v4) + Supabase (PostgreSQL + JWT Auth)  
> **Current State**: Expo 55 project with minimal scaffolding

---

## STEP 1 — Backend-to-Frontend Feature Map

### Core Domain Entities

| Entity | DB Table | PK Field | Key Relationships |
|--------|----------|----------|-------------------|
| Account | `accounts` | `id` (UUID) | Owns transactions via `from_account_id` / `to_account_id` |
| Transaction | `transactions` | `id` (UUID) | References accounts; stores income/expense/transfer |
| Goal | `goals` | `uuid` | Linked to user savings; prediction uses transaction history |
| Investment | `investments` | `uuid` | Has `investment_value_history`; cash-out creates income transaction |
| Cash Flow (legacy) | `cash_flow` | `uuid` | Legacy quick entry; analytics reads from `transactions` |

### Complete API → UI Feature Map

| UI Feature | API Endpoint | Method | Notes |
|------------|-------------|--------|-------|
| **Authentication** | | | |
| Sign Up | Supabase Auth SDK | — | `supabase.auth.signUp()` |
| Sign In | Supabase Auth SDK | — | `supabase.auth.signInWithPassword()` |
| Sign Out | Supabase Auth SDK | — | `supabase.auth.signOut()` |
| Token Refresh | Supabase Auth SDK | — | `supabase.auth.refreshSession()` |
| **Dashboard** | | | |
| Today's Summary Card | `/api/cashflows/analytics/today` | GET | Returns `{ inflow, outflow }` |
| Account Balances | `/api/accounts` | GET | Returns accounts with derived balances |
| Recent Transactions | `/api/cashflows/analytics/recent` | GET | Last 20 transactions in legacy format |
| Cash Flow Chart | `/api/cashflows/analytics/timeseries` | GET | `timeView`, `startDate`, `endDate` params |
| **Accounts** | | | |
| Account List | `/api/accounts` | GET | All accounts with computed balances |
| Account Detail | `/api/accounts/:id` | GET | Single account without balance |
| Account Balance | `/api/accounts/:id/balance` | GET | Derived balance only |
| **Transactions** | | | |
| Transaction List | `/api/transactions` | GET | Filters: `transaction_type`, `account_id`, date range, pagination |
| Add Income | `/api/transactions/income` | POST | `{ amount, to_account_id, date?, category?, description? }` |
| Add Expense | `/api/transactions/expense` | POST | `{ amount, from_account_id, date?, category?, description? }` |
| Add Transfer | `/api/transactions/transfer` | POST | `{ amount, from_account_id, to_account_id, date?, description? }` |
| Quick Entry (Legacy) | `/api/cashflows/quick-entry` | POST | `{ amount, type, category, selectedTags }` |
| **Analytics** | | | |
| Time Series Chart | `/api/cashflows/analytics/timeseries` | GET | Daily/weekly/monthly aggregation |
| Category Breakdown | `/api/cashflows/analytics/by-category` | GET | Spending/income by category with percentages |
| Today Summary | `/api/cashflows/analytics/today` | GET | Today's inflow vs. outflow |
| **Goals** | | | |
| Goal Prediction | `/api/goals/generate-prediction` | GET | `goalId` + `userId` → AI-powered forecast |
| **Investments** | | | |
| Portfolio List | `/api/investments` | GET | All investments with `absolute_gain`, `percentage_change` |
| Investment Detail | `/api/investments/:id` | GET | Full value history included |
| Create Investment | `/api/investments` | POST | Atomically creates record + expense transaction |
| Record Value | `/api/investments/:id/value` | POST | Updates current value + adds history |
| Cash Out | `/api/investments/:id/cashout` | POST | Reduces value + creates income transaction |
| Delete Investment | `/api/investments/:id` | DELETE | Removes record |

### Authentication Flow

```
Client → Supabase Auth SDK → JWT (access + refresh tokens)
Client → TrackiFi API with `Authorization: Bearer <token>`
API → Supabase `auth.getUser(token)` → RLS-scoped queries
```

- Access token expires in **1 hour**
- Refresh token lasts **60 days**
- On 401, auto-refresh and retry

### Pagination Pattern

- **Offset-based** for transactions: `limit` (default 20, max 100) + `offset`
- Analytics endpoints return fixed-size or full results (no pagination)
- No `meta` envelope currently; client must track pagination state

### Error Handling Shapes

| Source | Shape |
|--------|-------|
| App errors | `{ error: string }` |
| Zod validation | `{ success: false, error: { issues: [...], name: "ZodError" } }` |
| 404 catch-all | `{ error: "Not Found", path: string, method: string }` |
| Server errors | `{ error: string, stack?: string }` |

