### Component Hierarchy

#### Atoms (Primitives)
- `Text` — Themed text with variant prop
- `Button` — Primary, secondary, ghost, destructive variants
- `Input` — Text input with label, error state
- `Badge` — Status badges (income, expense, transfer, type)
- `Icon` — Wrapped icon set (Expo Symbols)
- `Divider` — Themed horizontal rule
- `Avatar` — User/entity avatar with initials fallback

#### Molecules (Composed)
- `AmountDisplay` — Formatted currency with +/− prefix and color
- `AccountCard` — Account name + type badge + balance
- `TransactionRow` — Category icon + description + amount + date
- `ProgressBar` — Linear progress with percentage label
- `StatWidget` — Label + value + optional change indicator
- `ChipFilter` — Filter tag with active/inactive states
- `EmptyState` — Illustration + message + CTA button

#### Organisms (Feature-Level)
- `BalanceSummary` — Total balance across all accounts
- `TodaySummaryCard` — Inflow vs. outflow for today
- `TransactionList` — Infinite scrollable transaction list with grouping by date
- `TimeSeriesChart` — Bar/area chart for inflow/outflow/savings
- `CategoryPieChart` — Donut chart with ranked legend
- `InvestmentCard` — Investment name + type + value + gain/loss
- `GoalProgressCard` — Goal name + progress bar + prediction text
- `TransactionForm` — Tabbed form for income/expense/transfer creation
- `ValueHistoryChart` — Line chart for investment value over time

#### Templates (Layouts)
- `TabLayout` — Bottom tab bar with safe area
- `PageLayout` — Scroll view with header + content
- `BottomSheet` — Slide-up panel for forms and actions
- `ModalCard` — Centered modal for confirmations

