## STEP 6 — Data Integration Strategy

### API Client Structure

```typescript
// services/api-client.ts
class ApiClient {
  private baseUrl: string;
  private getToken: () => Promise<string | null>;

  async request<T>(endpoint: string, options?: RequestInit): Promise<T>;
  // Handles: auth headers, 401 retry with token refresh, error normalization
}
```

### Query Hooks (TanStack React Query)

| Hook | Endpoint | Query Key | Cache Time |
|------|----------|-----------|------------|
| `useAccounts()` | GET `/accounts` | `['accounts']` | 5 min |
| `useAccountBalance(id)` | GET `/accounts/:id/balance` | `['accounts', id, 'balance']` | 1 min |
| `useTransactions(filters)` | GET `/transactions` | `['transactions', filters]` | 2 min |
| `useCreateIncome()` | POST `/transactions/income` | Invalidates `['accounts', 'transactions', 'analytics']` | — |
| `useCreateExpense()` | POST `/transactions/expense` | Invalidates `['accounts', 'transactions', 'analytics']` | — |
| `useCreateTransfer()` | POST `/transactions/transfer` | Invalidates `['accounts', 'transactions']` | — |
| `useTodaySummary()` | GET `/analytics/today` | `['analytics', 'today']` | 30 sec |
| `useRecentTransactions()` | GET `/analytics/recent` | `['analytics', 'recent']` | 2 min |
| `useTimeSeries(params)` | GET `/analytics/timeseries` | `['analytics', 'timeseries', params]` | 10 min |
| `useCategoryBreakdown(params)` | GET `/analytics/by-category` | `['analytics', 'category', params]` | 10 min |
| `useGoalPrediction(goalId)` | GET `/goals/generate-prediction` | `['goals', goalId, 'prediction']` | 30 min |
| `useInvestments()` | GET `/investments` | `['investments']` | 5 min |
| `useInvestmentDetail(id)` | GET `/investments/:id` | `['investments', id]` | 5 min |
| `useCreateInvestment()` | POST `/investments` | Invalidates `['investments', 'accounts', 'transactions']` | — |
| `useRecordValue(id)` | POST `/investments/:id/value` | Invalidates `['investments']` | — |
| `useCashOut(id)` | POST `/investments/:id/cashout` | Invalidates `['investments', 'accounts', 'transactions']` | — |
| `useDeleteInvestment(id)` | DELETE `/investments/:id` | Invalidates `['investments']` | — |

### Cache Invalidation Strategy

Mutations automatically invalidate related queries:

| Mutation | Invalidated Queries |
|----------|-------------------|
| Create Income | `accounts`, `transactions`, `analytics.today`, `analytics.recent` |
| Create Expense | `accounts`, `transactions`, `analytics.today`, `analytics.recent`, `analytics.category` |
| Create Transfer | `accounts`, `transactions` |
| Create Investment | `investments`, `accounts`, `transactions` |
| Cash Out Investment | `investments`, `accounts`, `transactions` |
| Record Value | `investments` (detail + list) |
| Delete Investment | `investments` |

### Error Handling Strategy

```typescript
// types/api.ts
type ApiError =
  | { type: 'app'; error: string }
  | { type: 'validation'; issues: ZodIssue[] }
  | { type: 'auth'; error: string }
  | { type: 'network'; error: Error };

// Normalized by api-client.ts from raw API responses
```

