## STEP 9 — Development Roadmap

### Phase 1 — Foundation (Week 1-2) — Complexity: ⭐⭐

| Task | Detail |
|------|--------|
| Design tokens | `src/constants/tokens.ts` — colors, typography, spacing |
| Theme provider | `ThemeProvider` + `useTheme()` with dark/light mode |
| Atom components | `Text`, `Button`, `Input`, `Badge`, `Divider` |
| API client | `api-client.ts` with auth headers, retry, error normalization |
| TypeScript types | All types from `src/types/` mirroring backend schemas |
| Query provider | TanStack React Query client setup |

### Phase 2 — Authentication (Week 3) — Complexity: ⭐⭐

| Task | Detail |
|------|--------|
| Supabase client | Initialize with `SUPABASE_URL` + `SUPABASE_ANON_KEY` |
| Auth store | Zustand store: session, signIn, signUp, signOut |
| AuthGuard | Route layout that redirects unauthenticated users |
| Login page | Email + password form with validation |
| Register page | Sign up form with email confirmation flow |
| Token management | Auto-refresh via `onAuthStateChange`, secure storage |

### Phase 3 — Dashboard (Week 4) — Complexity: ⭐⭐⭐

| Task | Detail |
|------|--------|
| Account hooks | `useAccounts()`, `useAccountBalance()` |
| Analytics hooks | `useTodaySummary()`, `useRecentTransactions()` |
| BalanceSummary | Total balance widget with account breakdown |
| TodaySummaryCard | Today's inflow vs outflow |
| RecentTransactions | Last 20 transactions list |
| Dashboard page | Compose all widgets with pull-to-refresh |

### Phase 4 — Transactions (Week 5-6) — Complexity: ⭐⭐⭐⭐

| Task | Detail |
|------|--------|
| Transaction hooks | `useTransactions()` with infinite query, `useCreateIncome()`, etc. |
| TransactionRow | Row component with type color, category, amount, date |
| TransactionList | Infinite scroll with date grouping |
| FilterBar | Type, account, date range filters |
| TransactionForm | Tabbed form (Income / Expense / Transfer) in bottom sheet |
| Optimistic updates | Immediate UI update before API confirmation |

### Phase 5 — Analytics (Week 7) — Complexity: ⭐⭐⭐

| Task | Detail |
|------|--------|
| Charter library setup | Install and configure charting library |
| TimeSeriesChart | Bar chart with inflow/outflow/savings series |
| CategoryPieChart | Donut chart with ranked category list |
| Analytics hooks | `useTimeSeries()`, `useCategoryBreakdown()` |
| Analytics page | Period selector + charts + drill-down |

### Phase 6 — Goals (Week 8) — Complexity: ⭐⭐⭐

| Task | Detail |
|------|--------|
| Goal hooks | `useGoalPrediction()` |
| GoalProgressCard | Progress bar + name + target |
| PredictionWidget | AI-generated prediction text + estimated date |
| Goal pages | List + detail with prediction |

### Phase 7 — Investments (Week 9-10) — Complexity: ⭐⭐⭐⭐

| Task | Detail |
|------|--------|
| Investment hooks | `useInvestments()`, `useInvestmentDetail()`, mutations |
| PortfolioSummary | Total value + total gain/loss |
