## Verification Plan

Since this is a **planning document** (not a code implementation), verification consists of:

### Structural Verification
- Confirm every backend endpoint documented in `docs/api/` has a corresponding entry in the Feature Map (Step 1)
- Confirm all TypeScript interfaces in `09-data-models.md` have corresponding types in the `src/types/` plan
- Confirm caching strategies match the recommended durations in `10-mobile-integration.md`

### Manual Verification (User Review)
- Review this plan for completeness, accuracy, and alignment with product vision
- Verify navigation structure matches desired user flow
- Confirm design system tokens match brand guidelines
- Validate the phased roadmap against team capacity and priorities
